column5: Sinclair,  Every time I see one of your post that "Name" kept sticking in my head and I couldn't figure out why.... until I seen this photo on TV and it jogged my memory of years past.....always loved those signs.
You could always claim that your a distance relation and now want your dues....like the idiot from facebook......he was from the Wellsville area where I went to college...
You went to College ??  The odds makers take a beating again

A redneck family's only son returns home from college. The father asks, "Well son, you done gone to college, so you must be perty smart. Why don't you speak some math fer' us?"  The son says, "Pi R squared."  The father yells, "Why son, they ain't teached ya nothin'! Pies are round, cornbread are square."
I don't care who you are that's funny!:rofl2:
